<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='738204' id='t-738204'>In other words, they were fixed in the concrete</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='741720' id='t-741720'>mores and attitudes they had inherited.</span>
