<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='780335' id='t-780335'>Or take an Islamic father whose daughter has been raped,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='783702' id='t-783702'>and he feels he's honor-bound to kill her.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='786912' id='t-786912'>Well, he's treating his mores</span>
